name: "Water" the second element
description: THE FIVE ELEMENTS SERIES Water  Free NFT “Aether” when you collect all the five elemental nfts  elements after this one (DM wallett address if you collect all five) Water is the element of emotion and the unconscious, as opposed to the conscious intellectualism of air.
